name: Community Survey Summary Results - 2012 to 2018
description: The Office of Internal Audit (OIA) conducts an annual survey of Chattanooga residents to gather their views of city services. This dataset is a summary file of the overall satisfaction scores from 2012 to 2018.  - See more at: http://www.chattanooga.gov/internal-audit/community-surveys
